<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.2.10">
<l>talaippey kāla namaṉṟamar pācam viṭṭā</l>
<l>lalaippū ṇuṇṇumav vallalel lāmakalak</l>
<l>kalaippaṉ ñāṉatteṉ kaṇṇaṉaik kaṇṭukoṇṭu</l>
<l>nilaippeṟ ṟeṉṉeñcam peṟṟatu nīṭuyirē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>So that, at the time of meeting, if Yama lets go of the snare on his people,</l>
<l>all that unhappiness departs that eats [my] troubled flesh,</l>
<l>having obtained a position by seeing for myself my Kṛṣṇa with the knowledge</l>
<l>of many arts, my heart has obtained long life.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
